<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-28 01:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0876 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r s BC-BBO-SERIES-LEDE-TEX     10-28 0768
