   DRUG-RESISTANT-TB (Undated) _ Scientific experts say that
strains of tuberculosis resistant to various drugs are spreading
faster than anticipated overseas and that a new treatment strategy
is needed to prevent an epidemic from spinning out of control. By
Judith Miller.
