   TRAVEL
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-PHILLY _ PHILADELPHIA _ Remember the kid who was a head
taller than everybody else in seventh grade? The one who had hair
on his chest and could carry five classmates on his back during
playground football? Remember how he stopped growing that year, and
everybody else shot past him, and all through high school he wore
that sneer of aggression to hide his insecurity? Think of that kid
the next time you're in Philadelphia and this city will make sense.
For a few brief, shining moments, The City of Brotherly Love was
that kid. (Belkin, Palm Beach Post). MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   PHILLY-SPEAK _ Dictionary of words and phrases that may need
translation. MOVED.
