through the character of Joshua, who recurs in several of Girzone's
novels, the latest of which is Joshua: The Homecoming (Doubleday,
$19.95). Joshua is a mysterious woodcarver who appears suddenly in
different contemporary settings, and endears people to him with his
simple and loving ways. (Dayton Daily News). 17.
