<HEADER>
A1101 &Cx1f; tad-z
r f BC-GEEWAX-Y2K-COLUMN-COX     10-28 0624
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GEEWAX-Y2K-COLUMN-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FOR HOUSE Y2K WATCHER, IT'S TIME TO WAIT AND SEE
 &HT;    Moving in (k) commentary and (f) financial categories for
release Sunday, Oct. 31.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
