<HEADLINE>
CYBER-CALIFORNIANS, HUNGARIAN SOFTWARE REBUILD QUAKE-TORN TURKEY  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: San Diego, CALIF. and Nashville, TENN.)   (This 325-word ``separate buy'' article is from the International
Herald Tribune.)  
  
