Lewis Brown Jr., who entered office as Mr. San Francisco, as
colorful and irrepressible as the city considers itself, has
disappointed voters on all sides. By Evelyn Nieves.
</P>
<P>
   SCI-FLOWER-ORIGINS (Undated) _ After more than a hundred years
of arguing, theorizing and banging their heads against the wall,
evolutionary biologists have at last solved a puzzle considered so
difficult that Darwin himself called it the ``abominable mystery.''
How, biologists have long wondered, did the world's flowering
plants _ the most diverse and important group of plants on earth _
first evolve? By Carol Kaesuk Yoon.
