<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-28 16:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1456 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r s BC-FBN-JOE-MONTANA-HNS &LR;      10-28 0507
