 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    TEXACO'S BILLION DOLLAR BET ON BRAZIL'S DEEP WATER FRADE FIELD.
Texaco is making a billion-dollar bet on Brazil to boost its
maturing reserves _ and keep its shareholders happy.
