</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PATCO-SUIT29-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FIRED PATCO WORKERS SUE FOR OLD AIR CONTROLLER JOBS
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By JULIA MALONE
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
