   ECON-REPORT (Undated) _ The American economy turned in its best
quarterly performance of the year this summer, virtually
guaranteeing enough momentum to carry the nation to its longest
economic expansion in history early in the year 2000. By Louis
Uchitelle.
</P>
<P>
   With graphic.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 8:15 p.m. ET in ``f'' news file.)
