is is just one of several anti-American murals painted on the walls
of the old U.S. Embassy in the Iranian capital. The embassy, where
American hostages were kept for 444 days, is now a military high
school for the Iranian Revolutionary Guard. (Larry Kaplow/Cox News
Service)
