executive director of the Naval Safety Center from his office in
Norfolk. ``All we do is advise. I don't have the power here to
enforce. ... I have the power of moral persuasion. Unlike the
Federal Aviation Administration, which monitors civilian aviation
safety, the Naval Safety Center cannot mandate safety changes. ``I
don't direct anything. Nobody here directs anything.'' (Rick
McKay/Cox News Service Photo)
