Knight pilot and until June the director of aviation safety at the
Naval Safety Center. ``If it's a high risk that's going to happen
often, it gets fixed. That's the bottom line.'' The Daily News
examination found that problems such as those involving the Sea
Knight hydraulic system often continue. (Rick McKay/Cox News
Service Photo)
