</P>
<P>
   (NYT2) NEW YORK -- Oct. 28, 1999 -- DEAD-THEATER-REVIEW, 10-28
-- Blair Brown and Christopher Walken in ``James Joyce's 'The
Dead,'''which opened Wednesday night at Playwrights Horizons. In
reconceiving Joyce's great, elegiac tale of a Christmastime
gathering in gaslight-era Dublin, this production achieves a
soft-spoken, hesitant air of intimacy that has you leaning forward
like a fascinated eavesdropper. (Sara Krulwich/New York Times
Photo)
