<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-28 22:22 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1796 &Cx1f; tta-z
u p BC-REPUBS-DEBATE-700&AMP;ADD     10-28 1121
